d of the very near future in which cattle, fish, and even the family pet can be cloned. But cloning humans is illegal - that is until family man Adam Gibson comes home from work one day to find a clone has replaced him. Taken from his family and plunged into a sinister world he doesn't understand, Gibson must not only save himself from the assassins who must destroy him to protect their secret, but uncover who and what is behind the horrible things happening to him.","genre_ids":[878,28,9648,18,53],"popularity":4.0681,"vote_count":2206,"poster_path":"/rODFJOFiPk1UVCe4pmBza8T6feO.jpg","release_date":"2000-11-17","vote_average":5.99,"backdrop_path":"/opkt6IK1Os5gAwhlpu27bCZCk8K.jpg","original_title":"The 6th Day","original_language":"en"},{"id":8460,"adult":false,"title":"The Skulls II","video":false,"overview":"After joining the Skulls, Ryan Sommers (Robin Dunne) is warned not to betray any secrets about the organization or its high-powered members. However, when Ryan witnesses a murder within the Skulls' private chambers, he finds that the closer he gets to revealing the truth - the more dangerous life becomes.","genre_ids":[28,53],"popularity":0.5841,"vote_count":81,"poster_path":"/h6atL0SP5qg6TXOXy9DklZgObn2.jpg","release_date":"2002-04-09","vote_average":4.71,"backdrop_path":"/sAFqN4bDfGUBgS6h323F7YcwqPe.jpg","original_title":"The Skulls II","original_language":"en"},{"id":8461,"adult":false,"title":"Funny Games","video":false,"overview":"When Ann, husband George, and son Georgie arrive at their holiday home they are visited by a pair of polite and seemingly pleasant young men. Armed with deceptively sweet smiles and some golf clubs, they proceed to terrorize and torture the tight-knit clan, giving them until the next day to survive.","genre_ids":[53,27],"popularity":4.9356,"vote_count":2217,"poster_path":"/zs92sAOh3Q0kDIJkgaJFTBzSFka.jpg","release_date":"2008-03-14","vote_average":6.556,"backdrop_path":"/6P4R7kYUdJprHpyBmOQO6aB85xX.jpg","original_title":"Funny Games","original_language":"en"},{"id":8536,"adult":false,"title":"Superman II","video":false,"overview":"Three Kryptonian criminals led by General Zod team up with Lex Luthor to conquer Earth, forcing a depowered Superman to regain his strength and stop them.","genre_ids":[878,28,12],"popularity":3.931,"vote_count":2467,"poster_path":"/3xk5cno9BHcnwc97XO9k21aI1Zi.jpg","release_date":"1980-12-12","vote_average":6.749,"backdrop_path":"/e77VeVcrXhxfCdJWD9rameYn7Qn.jpg","original_title":"Superman II","original_language":"en"},{"id":8555,"adult":false,"title":"Creep","video":false,"overview":"Trapped in a London subway station, a woman who's being pursued by a potential attacker heads into the unknown labyrinth of tunnels beneath the city's streets","genre_ids":[27,53,9648],"popularity":1.7095,"vote_count":824,"poster_path":"/w5oxV6MDEfL48FMK9BmYTD2wQRm.jpg","release_date":"2004-08-10","vote_average":5.998,"backdrop_path":"/ooPtDdWP2nuYCoyLJAVwdthf5dN.jpg","original_title":"Creep","original_language":"en"},{"id":8247,"adult":false,"title":"Jumper","video":false,"overview":"David Rice is a man who knows no boundaries, a Jumper, born with the uncanny ability to teleport instantly to anywhere on Earth. When he discovers others like himself, David is thrust into a dangerous and bloodthirsty war while being hunted by a sinister and determined group of zealots who have sworn to destroy all Jumpers. Now, David’s extraordinary gift may be his only hope for survival!","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":6.5744,"vote_count":6112,"poster_path":"/3pPZ9JhNz3VMmASVir5SMHvTDUU.jpg","release_date":"2008-02-13","vote_average":6.157,"backdrop_path":"/25OT7Xp6juYNXQVkaxfKpj3ZoPF.jpg","original_title":"Jumper","original_language":"en"},{"id":8270,"adult":false,"title":"The Lookout","video":false,"overview":"Chris is a once promising high school athlete whose life is turned upside down following a tragic accident. As he tries to maintain a normal life, he takes a job as a janitor at a bank, where he ultimately finds himself caught up in a planned heist.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":1.0443,"vote_count":689,"poster_path":"/wTYyXCoIBy2TDxetoGS4Sc0VBP1.jpg","release_date":"2007-03-09","vote_average":6.666,"backdrop_path":"/4iEg0LWTx9aTWOWMhpBu3UffXih.jpg","original_title":"The Lookout","original_language":"en"},{"id":8271,"adult":false,"title":"Disturbia","video":false,"overview":"Kale has a life most teenagers would envy. He spends his days endlessly playing video games, surfing the net, eating junk food and watching cable. He has complete free reign of the house, and a beautiful young hottie named Ashley has just moved in next door. There’s only one problem—he’s not allowed to leave the house. Kale’s under court-ordered house arrest for three months, and if he takes one step beyond a 100-foot perimeter of the house, his next confinement will be in a real prison.","genre_ids":[53,18,9648],"popularity":4.1334,"vote_count":4000,"poster_path":"/3f9KwSrieczuH9nRrwfOsoMoMNd.jpg","release_date":"2007-03-27","vote_average":6.684,"backdrop_path":"/7bnZEVPcdSMySabQQJWTqBGUDP.jpg","original_title":"Disturbia","original_language":"en"},{"id":8289,"adult":false,"title":"Gorky Park","video":false,"overview":"Police Inspector Renko tries to solve the case of three bodies found in Moscow's Gorky Park but finds his attempts to solve the crime impeded by his superiors. Working on his own, Renko seeks out more information and stumbles across a conspiracy involving the highest levels of the government.","genre_ids":[53,80,18,9648],"popularity":1.315,"vote_count":334,"poster_path":"/xQFH7XlMk8pLPDzK5XVEj5McsRm.jpg","release_date":"1983-12-15","vote_average":6.323,"backdrop_path":"/dO8qUkabhQwBy8lPGawtvWQkdKd.jpg","original_title":"Gorky Park","original_language":"en"},{"id":8645,"adult":false,"title":"The Happening","video":false,"overview":"When a deadly airborne virus threatens to wipe out the northeastern United States, teacher Elliot Moore and his wife Alma flee from contaminated cities into the countryside in a fight to discover the truth. Is it terrorism, the accidental release of some toxic military bio weapon -- or something even more sinister?","genre_ids":[53,878],"popularity":5.2526,"vote_count":3877,"poster_path":"/fP4nBrtmc0teSDDHzYmDE7TLQBT.jpg","release_date":"2008-06-11","vote_average":5.395,"backdrop_path":"/6moXpp6y1EZ6pfnSxnKFMrbFnWv.jpg","original_title":"The Happening","original_language":"en"},{"id":8653,"adult":false,"title":"The Isle","video":false,"overview":"Mute Hee-Jin is working as a clerk in a fishing resort in the Korean wilderness; selling baits, food and occasionally her body to the fishing tourists. One day she falls in love with Hyun-Shik, who is on the run from the police, and rescues him with a fish hook when he tries to commit suicide.","genre_ids":[18,53],"popularity":1.812,"vote_count":361,"poster_path":"/sZZ7VOFVpAN4IrPiYJzvuoVowRW.jpg","release_date":"2000-04-22","vote_average":6.917,"backdrop_path":"/kUM5b2y1eveCOINZmq6FWFb2Iob.jpg","original_title":"섬","original_language":"ko"},{"id":8688,"adult":false,"title":"Snake Eyes","video":false,"overview":"All bets are off when shady homicide cop Rick Santoro witnesses a murder during a boxing match. Determined to solve the crime, he quickly learns that his search for answers will only uncover yet more questions in an ever-widening web of conspiracy, intrigue, and danger.","genre_ids":[80,9648,53],"popularity":2.6082,"vote_count":1476,"poster_path":"/gsh9mQKRrr4M90XC9Rr0wxefc9u.jpg","release_date":"1998-08-07","vote_average":6.182,"backdrop_path":"/2MvYDk1CzVOffa6IoFjVrTR3Ow4.jpg","original_title":"Snake Eyes","original_language":"en"},{"id":8436,"adult":false,"title":"The Page Turner","video":false,"overview":"Mélanie Prouvost, a ten-year-old butcher's daughter, is a gifted pianist. That is why she and her parents decide that she sit for the Conservatory entrance exam. Although Mélanie is very likely to be admitted, she unfortunately gets distracted by the president of the jury's offhand attitude and she fails. Ten years later, Mélanie becomes her page turner, waiting patiently for her revenge.","genre_ids":[18,10402,53],"popularity":0.4351,"vote_count":145,"poster_path":"/lBomGoLZKklJWb5hMvcy44WbUsd.jpg","release_date":"2006-08-09","vote_average":6.521,"backdrop_path":"/uyZMq9VTihrWBVXzIQUkB8P8Nnq.jpg","original_title":"La Tourneuse de pages","original_language":"fr"},{"id":8316,"adult":false,"title":"The Countess","video":false,"overview":"Kingdom of Hungary, 17th century. As she gets older, powerful Countess Erzsébet Báthory (1560-1614), blinded by the passion that she feels for a younger man, succumbs to the mad delusion that blood will keep her young and beautiful forever.","genre_ids":[18,36,53,9648,27],"popularity":1.0434,"vote_count":179,"poster_path":"/nnksbKPiwDZS5x9O64OU94hJ15g.jpg","release_date":"2009-03-13","vote_average":5.907,"backdrop_path":"/w1kShva9ltxozY2UePgBjXjedvI.jpg","original_title":"The Countess","original_language":"en"},{"id":8333,"adult":false,"title":"The Taking of Pelham One Two Three","video":false,"overview":"In New York, armed men hijack a subway car and demand a ransom for the passengers. Even if it's paid, how could they get away?","genre_ids":[80,53,28],"popularity":1.421,"vote_count":605,"poster_path":"/vNhywp9w1DVG6BytxKp4kjtaaGC.jpg","release_date":"1974-10-02","vote_average":7.4,"backdrop_path":"/wDLUp63wIE6NeWHAcJkCijhI3M8.jpg","original_title":"The Taking of Pelham One Two Three","original_language":"en"},{"id":8744,"adult":false,"title":"Albino Alligator","video":false,"overview":"While escaping from a foiled robbery attempt, three thieves find themselves surrounded by police at a New Orleans bar--only they're not the people the police are searching for.","genre_ids":[80,18,53],"popularity":0.6639,"vote_count":160,"poster_path":"/jOyV5Rb1MaMUl6XrWWossVTm7BA.jpg","release_date":"1997-01-17","vote_average":5.731,"backdrop_path":"/vcafO6dnQT9bCXRwwZijkYHW9Q0.j